  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The kidnapper speaks to you through a handheld radio transceiver. Since the kidnapper does not use a cell phone, it is impossible to trace his call signals through cell towers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras/3437e1a426ca8b520c4e3f31b7354c30.avif?t=1743170117\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras_big/3437e1a426ca8b520c4e3f31b7354c30.avif?t=1743170117 width=800 height=432 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are forced to carry out various instructions by the kidnapper to prolong the life of your wife and daughter, which will take you through a long and dangerous night from 8pm to 4am.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras/70b83319086854c12e94e09ba1d980d1.poster.avif?t=1743170117\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras/70b83319086854c12e94e09ba1d980d1.webm?t=1743170117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras/70b83319086854c12e94e09ba1d980d1.mp4?t=1743170117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are gifted with a photographic memory. While you are carrying out the demands of the kidnapper, uncover clues in your surroundings to track down your family and rescue them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras/e2f326ce163037742a45ba401c016cba.poster.avif?t=1743170117\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras/e2f326ce163037742a45ba401c016cba.webm?t=1743170117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras/e2f326ce163037742a45ba401c016cba.mp4?t=1743170117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your life will be put at risk of a variety of threats. Stealth mechanics are present. You must be stealthy as you are observant.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras/9f78ccb814d86c2e65e5fc9bdd243059.poster.avif?t=1743170117\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras/9f78ccb814d86c2e65e5fc9bdd243059.webm?t=1743170117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras/9f78ccb814d86c2e65e5fc9bdd243059.mp4?t=1743170117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game requires attention to detail and critical thinking. You have been warned.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The kidnapper speaks to you through a handheld radio transceiver. Since the kidnapper does not use a cell phone, it is impossible to trace his call signals through cell towers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras/3437e1a426ca8b520c4e3f31b7354c30.avif?t=1743170117\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras_big/3437e1a426ca8b520c4e3f31b7354c30.avif?t=1743170117 width=800 height=432 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are forced to carry out various instructions by the kidnapper to prolong the life of your wife and daughter, which will take you through a long and dangerous night from 8pm to 4am.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras/70b83319086854c12e94e09ba1d980d1.poster.avif?t=1743170117\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras/70b83319086854c12e94e09ba1d980d1.webm?t=1743170117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487620/extras/70b83319086854c12e94e09ba1d980d1.mp4?t=1743170117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are gifted with a photographic memory. While you are carrying out the demands of the kidnapper, uncover clues in your surroundings to track down your family and rescue them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets